How To Learn A New Skill ?

* This is important,beacuse it saves time, apko manzil tak jaldi pohancha det ahi ,agar ap systematic manner se seekhein.
* Agar ap galat tareeke se skill seekhein gaye , oh maybe ap 1,2 mahine mein jakar woh skill seekehin gaye.
* Skill woh pick krein jo apke goal ke saath align ho.
* Self Analysis krein, khud ko dekhein, kya apko video dekhna zyada pasand hai ya article pdhna zyada pasand hai,kya apko crowd mein ksi leader ki discussion sunna zyada pasand hai ,ya apko audio speech zyada pasand hai.
* Agar apko video dekhna pasand hai ,to youtube par search krein ,videos dekhein, digiskills paltform provide you vast resources about courses,peeche poori team hai jo jawaab bhi deti hai.
* Study The Greats, Do the Practice, kamyaab logon ki zindagi ke baaray mein padhain, or jo unhone kiya us pr practice krein.
* Teach ,jab ap seekhein toh dusron ko sikhayein, isse ap jo skill seekh rahay hai woh mazeed behtar hujayega.
* Test Yourself ,apne doston azeezzon se feedback lein ,apko idea ap kitna dur hai ,apko kitni or mehnat krni hai, apko pata chalega toh skill jaldi develop krein gaye.
* Kbhi bhi yeh nahi smjhiye ga jo apne kahin se ksi bhi platform se seekh liya yehi sb kuch ,apne andar curiosity rkhein nayi cheezon ko seekhne ki.

